messages.errorUploading: An error occurred while uploading the file.
messages.errorReading: An error occurred while reading the file.
messages.uploadPaused: Pausing upload while contacts are imported.

explanations.contactGroup: Assigns all contacts in CSV file to the selected group. Leave empty to skip assignment.
explanations.recipientList: Assigns all contacts in CSV file to the selected recipient list. Leave empty to skip assignment.
explanations.delimiter: The delimiter for CSV row data items.
explanations.batchSize: The number of records that will be uploaded and processed at a time.
